{{flavour|This invocation calls forth an avatar of battle and bloodshed, mirroring sufficiently damaging attacks and spells of the invoker and their nearby allies.}}

'''Grand Avatar''' is a monster-only spell that conjures a [[Grand avatar (monster)|grand avatar]] monster.

Monsters that can cast this spell include:

* {{monsterlink|Warmonger}}

==History==
*Removed in [[0.17]].
*Grand Avatar was added in [[0.14]].

